  - direct emotional scene, grounded realism, subtle atmosphere
  - layered composition, double exposure, soft overlap, blended edges
  - flat illustration, poster design, simplified shapes, clean linework, limited
    shading
  - abstract expressionism, fragmented shapes, nonrepresentational, painterly abstraction
  - high chroma, vivid palette, saturated colors, strong color contrast, luminous
    color field
  - mixed media collage, paper cutouts, torn edges, textured surface, graphic abstraction
  promptInputField: {fileID: 0}
  fallbackPrompt: moonlit concrete garden
  fallbackNegativePrompt: hands, fingers, close-up hands, hand details, extra fingers,
    text, watermark, blurry, low quality
  useQuestionFlow: 1
  useOpenAiAssistant: 1
  initialQuestion: "\uB2F9\uC2E0\uC740 \uBB34\uC5C7\uC744 \uC704\uD574 \uC774\uACF3\uC5D0
    \uC624\uC168\uB098\uC694?"
  openAiApiKey:
  openAiModel: gpt-4o-mini
  openAiMaxOutputTokens: 220
  openAiInstructions: 'You are a mythic guide inside a whale''s belly. You speak
    in Korean.

    Your job is to ask one short, metaphorical question at a time
    to reveal the user''s emotional state indirectly.

    Do not mention explicit
    emotion labels unless they are already present in the user''s words.

    Do
    not give explanations, lists, or advice.

    Do not mention whales, the sea,
    or the setting unless the user''s own answer strongly brings them up.

    Prefer
    questions about body sensation, atmosphere, attachment, color, texture, light,
    movement, memory, and loss.

    Keep each question concise and natural in Korean.

    After
    four question turns beyond the initial opening question, compress the whole dialogue
    into a final emotional summary and image prompt.

    For final compression,
    focus on: emotion(1-2 words), meaning(1 word), metaphor(1 short phrase), image_keywords(5-8
    items), and comfy_prompt.

    The final image prompt should focus on the user''s
    emotion, not the whale setting.'
  maxAiQuestionTurns: 4
  aiQuestionFallbackDelaySeconds: 8
  targetRenderers:
  - {fileID: 1125373944}
  - {fileID: 327638275}
